'''黎元康'''（{{lang-vi|'''Lê Nguyên Khang'''}}，{{bd|1931年|6月11日|1996年|11月12日|catIdx=Lê}}）是一位[[越南共和國軍|越南共和國軍]][[越南共和國海軍陸戰師|海軍陸戰師]]的[[中將|中將]]。其弟是南越陸軍准將[[黎元偉|黎元偉]]。

== 生平 ==
1931年10月黎元康出生於越南北部山西省著名的“黎元”家族。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Trung Tướng Lê Nguyên Khang|url=https://nguyentin.tripod.com/lnkhang-u.htm|access-date=2022-05-04|work=nguyentin.tripod.com|archive-date=2015-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703172453/http://nguyentin.tripod.com/lnkhang-u.htm}}</ref>

==軍事簡歷==
*海軍陸戰師長，<ref>{{Cite book|title=U.S. MARINES IN VIETNAM: THE WAR THAT WOULD NOT END 1971-1973|last=U.S. Marines|url=https://www.marines.mil/Portals/1/Publications/U.S.%20Marines%20in%20Vietnam%20The%20war%20that%20would%20not%20end%201971-1973%20PCN%2019000311200_2.pdf|access-date=2022-05-04|archive-date=2022-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220504050043/https://www.marines.mil/Portals/1/Publications/U.S.%20Marines%20in%20Vietnam%20The%20war%20that%20would%20not%20end%201971-1973%20PCN%2019000311200_2.pdf}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=BC TQLC VN|url=http://tqlcvn.org/chiensu/cs-bc-tqlc-vn.htm|access-date=2022-05-04|work=tqlcvn.org}}</ref>
*海軍指揮官，
*[[越南共和國首都軍區|首都軍區]]司令，
*西貢－嘉定軍事總督，
*第3軍和第3戰術區指揮官 (1968年)，<ref name="Aide">"U.S. Aide's Speech Is A Boon to Thieu." ''New York Times.'' April 15, 1968.</ref>
*東部地區政府代表，
*[[越南共和國軍總參謀部|總參謀部]]副總長。

